# Iowa Liquor Sales data analysis


## Overview

Here we explore open available data from the Iowa Open Data portal. We explore the dataset "Iowa Liquor Sales." You can check it [here](https://data.iowa.gov/Sales-Distribution/Iowa-Liquor-Sales/m3tr-qhgy/about_data).
